1
00:00:06,042 --> 00:00:07,500
[PREVIOUSLY]
Congratulations, Wutong.

2
00:00:07,917 --> 00:00:10,207
My Title will be "Dragon Butterfly."

3
00:00:10,542 --> 00:00:11,999
Xuan Lao, you've broken through?

4
00:00:12,333 --> 00:00:14,291
What I must tell you now

5
00:00:14,583 --> 00:00:17,332
is another method to condense
the second Soul Core.

6
00:00:17,917 --> 00:00:19,541
I'm going to see that person again.

7
00:00:19,833 --> 00:00:23,207
The other reason I gathered you
is for an extremely important matter.

8
00:00:23,583 --> 00:00:25,332
Assassinate Xu Tianran.

9
00:00:26,167 --> 00:00:28,166
The child is teachable.

10
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:31,207
This is Sky Sun Douluo,
from the Dou Ling Empire.

11
00:00:31,417 --> 00:00:35,041
Now that everyone is here,
let us discuss the operation plan.

12
00:00:35,042 --> 00:00:36,042
Now that everyone is here,
let's discuss the action plan.

13
00:00:45,917 --> 00:00:48,374
The operation is codenamed
"Operation Destroy Emperor."

14
00:00:49,542 --> 00:00:51,374
Although Xu Tianran is young,

15
00:00:51,625 --> 00:00:53,166
he is a true warlord.

16
00:00:53,833 --> 00:00:57,207
As long as he lives,
future war is inevitable.

17
00:00:57,875 --> 00:00:59,832
But if we can assassinate Xu Tianran,

18
00:01:00,250 --> 00:01:02,124
the Sun-Moon Empire will surely plunge
into internal chaos.

19
00:01:02,708 --> 00:01:04,124
His several brothers

20
00:01:04,208 --> 00:01:06,332
will inevitably start
a succession struggle.

21
00:01:06,875 --> 00:01:09,249
After all, Xu Tianran's son
was just born.

22
00:01:09,625 --> 00:01:11,291
He is too young to stabilize the throne.

23
00:01:12,333 --> 00:01:14,624
Xu Tianran has a son? Then doesn't that mean...

24
00:01:15,375 --> 00:01:18,332
Whoever helps me avenge my father
will be my benefactor.

25
00:01:18,875 --> 00:01:21,666
Xu Tianran is not your father.

26
00:01:22,542 --> 00:01:24,999
Sister Orange, why torment yourself so?

27
00:01:25,792 --> 00:01:27,541
Our spies in the Sun-Moon Empire

28
00:01:27,583 --> 00:01:28,874
recently brought news

29
00:01:29,333 --> 00:01:30,333
that in seven days,

30
00:01:30,417 --> 00:01:34,332
Xu Tianran will serve as the chief officiant
at the Sun-Moon Empire's
Sacrifice to Heaven ceremony.

31
00:01:34,917 --> 00:01:36,749
That is our optimal timing.

32
00:01:37,708 --> 00:01:39,207
The altar is located
in the southern suburbs of Mingdu.

33
00:01:39,708 --> 00:01:41,791
To lure Xu Tianran's surrounding experts away,

34
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,541
we need a feint to the east,
striking in the west.

35
00:01:44,333 --> 00:01:46,499
Our target is here.

36
00:01:47,333 --> 00:01:49,749
This is the largest arsenal
in Mingdu.

37
00:01:50,417 --> 00:01:52,791
The fifteen Titled Douluo
from our three nations

38
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,082
will be divided into two teams.

39
00:01:54,542 --> 00:01:57,249
Senior Sky Sun will lead one team
to attack this arsenal,

40
00:01:57,333 --> 00:02:00,207
creating a disturbance to draw away
Xu Tianran's nearby experts.

41
00:02:01,042 --> 00:02:03,291
Senior Ontology will lead
four Titled Douluo

42
00:02:03,542 --> 00:02:05,707
to prepare for the thunderous strike
against Xu Tianran.

43
00:02:06,042 --> 00:02:08,249
This action plan is far too crude.

44
00:02:09,042 --> 00:02:11,332
The Sun-Moon Empire possesses
two Limit Douluo!

45
00:02:11,708 --> 00:02:12,874
Even if one is lured away,

46
00:02:13,083 --> 00:02:16,332
the remaining one is still enough to handle
Du Bubai and the four Super Douluo.

47
00:02:17,125 --> 00:02:20,791
Furthermore, an arsenal explosion
wouldn't attract that many experts.

48
00:02:20,792 --> 00:02:21,792
Yuhao,

49
00:02:21,875 --> 00:02:22,957
your task

50
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:26,041
is to lead everyone into
the Sun-Moon Empire.

51
00:02:26,333 --> 00:02:29,041
Once you enter Mingdu,
your mission ends.

52
00:02:31,417 --> 00:02:32,666
Entering Mingdu shouldn't be difficult.

53
00:02:33,125 --> 00:02:35,124
However, I hope that until we reach Mingdu,

54
00:02:36,208 --> 00:02:37,624
at the very least,

55
00:02:37,958 --> 00:02:39,249
everyone will follow my command.

56
00:02:44,875 --> 00:02:47,957
Only then can I guarantee
I will lead everyone to their positions.

57
00:02:48,875 --> 00:02:50,124
Follow your command?

58
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:53,124
Kid, how old are you exactly?

59
00:02:54,833 --> 00:02:58,541
Age brings wisdom. In terms of stealth,
we admit we are inferior to Yuhao.

60
00:02:58,542 --> 00:02:59,874
We are not as skilled as him.

61
00:03:00,208 --> 00:03:03,082
I agree to let him command
before we enter Mingdu.

62
00:03:06,417 --> 00:03:09,874
Kid, are you so confident?

63
00:03:11,083 --> 00:03:13,374
I also agree to let Huo Yuhao command.

64
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,500
Brother Du,

65
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:20,874
there's no time to delay.

66
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,999
We set out first thing tomorrow morning.

67
00:03:29,667 --> 00:03:30,249
Yuhao.

68
00:03:37,875 --> 00:03:39,166
Come, sit.

69
00:03:41,708 --> 00:03:44,374
This operation is very dangerous,
Yuhao.

70
00:03:44,708 --> 00:03:46,791
If your role weren't so critical,

71
00:03:47,208 --> 00:03:50,207
I would never have asked Shrek Academy
to let you come.

72
00:03:50,667 --> 00:03:51,667
Remember this:

73
00:03:52,125 --> 00:03:55,249
Your task is solely to bring them safely
into Mingdu.

74
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,041
Hiding your identity is sufficient.

75
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:01,207
When they act, you do not participate.

76
00:04:01,917 --> 00:04:03,291
If you sense the situation turning bad,

77
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,041
flee immediately.
Do not concern yourself with the others.

78
00:04:07,458 --> 00:04:09,582
My Lord Duke, why speak like this?

79
00:04:11,708 --> 00:04:13,457
I cannot explain much to you.

80
00:04:14,042 --> 00:04:17,166
Just remember to do as I say.

81
00:04:18,042 --> 00:04:20,874
Prioritize your own safety above all else.

82
00:04:24,875 --> 00:04:26,916
Alright, I understand.

83
00:04:29,042 --> 00:04:30,707
It seems this operation
has major issues.

84
00:04:31,208 --> 00:04:32,916
The White Tiger Duke is warning you.

85
00:04:35,708 --> 00:04:36,791
This "Destroy Emperor Operation"...

86
00:04:37,417 --> 00:04:39,416
there are details he cannot disclose.

87
00:04:39,875 --> 00:04:41,541
He seems to care for you deeply.

88
00:04:42,333 --> 00:04:45,374
Your hostility towards him
isn't as intense as before.

89
00:04:46,167 --> 00:04:47,457
Indeed.

90
00:04:47,458 --> 00:04:50,874
Though I'm unwilling to admit it,
that is the truth.

91
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:53,832
During the days you were missing,

92
00:04:54,333 --> 00:04:55,749
I returned to Star Luo City.

93
00:04:57,208 --> 00:05:00,624
I discovered he had restored
my mother's grave.

94
00:05:02,625 --> 00:05:05,374
Later, fighting in the Star Luo Empire,

95
00:05:05,917 --> 00:05:07,541
we interacted with him more frequently.

96
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:12,041
I have indeed changed my impression
of him somewhat.

97
00:05:12,065 --> 00:05:28,665
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

98
00:05:30,083 --> 00:05:31,083
Brother Du,

99
00:05:32,250 --> 00:05:35,374
you seem to value
that kid Huo Yuhao greatly.

100
00:05:36,625 --> 00:05:38,041
You are very tense.

101
00:05:39,875 --> 00:05:41,291
If not for that,

102
00:05:41,542 --> 00:05:43,957
you wouldn't fail to see that child's potential.

103
00:05:44,708 --> 00:05:47,666
His soul power is capped at Rank 89,

104
00:05:47,958 --> 00:05:51,957
yet his soul power intensity already rivals
that of a Titled Douluo.

105
00:05:52,542 --> 00:05:55,374
His spiritual power is comparable
to a Super Douluo.

106
00:05:55,875 --> 00:05:57,374
A Super Douluo?

107
00:05:58,375 --> 00:06:01,541
Moreover, he has already condensed
a Soul Core.

108
00:06:01,667 --> 00:06:03,124
With his talent,

109
00:06:03,375 --> 00:06:06,916
in less than ten years,
his cultivation will surpass yours.

110
00:06:07,958 --> 00:06:13,541
You are too impatient and restless;
your perception has declined drastically.

111
00:06:15,375 --> 00:06:16,375
Indeed.

112
00:06:16,875 --> 00:06:20,124
The national strength of the Dou Ling Empire
doesn't match the Tianhun Empire.

113
00:06:21,167 --> 00:06:23,916
If the Sun-Moon Empire redirects its offensive,

114
00:06:24,917 --> 00:06:27,791
Dou Ling Empire absolutely cannot hold.

115
00:06:28,708 --> 00:06:29,874
This operation...

116
00:06:30,208 --> 00:06:34,207
is gambling the future of the three original
Douluo nations.

117
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:38,124
Saying I'm not nervous would be a lie.

118
00:06:40,875 --> 00:06:44,499
I never expected we'd fall to such a state.

119
00:06:45,042 --> 00:06:46,249
There was a time

120
00:06:46,375 --> 00:06:50,541
I had absolute confidence
we could keep the enemy beyond our borders.

121
00:06:50,792 --> 00:06:52,249
But now it seems,

122
00:06:53,042 --> 00:06:54,707
how laughable that was.

123
00:06:55,292 --> 00:06:58,791
Being a frog in a well has left us
far too behind.

124
00:06:59,208 --> 00:07:01,082
We can only stake everything on this one throw.

125
00:07:01,833 --> 00:07:05,707
Brother Du, is the intelligence
from the Mingdu side reliable?

126
00:07:06,458 --> 00:07:07,791
Absolutely certain.

127
00:07:08,542 --> 00:07:11,832
Once you succeed, flee immediately.
Don't mind me.

128
00:07:12,875 --> 00:07:15,041
Alright. Be careful in everything.

129
00:07:43,583 --> 00:07:47,082
Sun-Moon scum! Blood debts
must be repaid in blood!

130
00:08:23,667 --> 00:08:25,332
Senior Du, take care on the road.

131
00:08:28,167 --> 00:08:31,541
Your Excellencies, I wish you a smooth journey
and a triumphant return.

132
00:08:32,208 --> 00:08:33,832
Return victorious soon.

133
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,500
Yuhao.

134
00:09:18,542 --> 00:09:19,332
We're at the border.

135
00:09:19,333 --> 00:09:19,707
We're at the border.

136
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:21,041
Spiritual Detection Shared.

137
00:09:27,375 --> 00:09:28,624
What powerful spiritual force.

138
00:09:29,083 --> 00:09:31,291
Extending vision across
the entire Mingdou Mountains.

139
00:09:31,958 --> 00:09:33,374
A 360-degree field with no blind spots.

140
00:09:33,375 --> 00:09:35,791
Every minute object is crystal clear.

141
00:09:36,917 --> 00:09:40,499
This kid's spiritual power
is truly unimaginable.

142
00:09:40,708 --> 00:09:43,249
Shrek Academy truly lives up to its name.

143
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:46,082
Worthy of being called
the Monster Academy.

144
00:09:46,125 --> 00:09:47,374
Impressive, Little Friend Huo.

145
00:09:47,958 --> 00:09:50,541
Sorry for raising my voice earlier;
please don't take offense.

146
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,000
You flatter me, Senior.

147
00:09:54,625 --> 00:09:56,374
Huo Yuhao's Spiritual Sharing

148
00:09:56,375 --> 00:09:59,749
not only assists fifteen Titled Douluo
simultaneously,

149
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:04,041
but also projects a unique action route
for each individual,

150
00:10:04,333 --> 00:10:05,707
each path not interfering
with the others.

151
00:10:06,208 --> 00:10:07,208
This is...

152
00:10:07,333 --> 00:10:10,666
Multitasking with terrifying
spiritual control.

153
00:10:10,958 --> 00:10:13,082
Your Eye of Destiny has awakened further.

154
00:10:14,167 --> 00:10:15,666
What a pity, what a pity.

155
00:10:16,375 --> 00:10:20,249
If only you had met this old man
a bit earlier,

156
00:10:20,583 --> 00:10:22,999
I would have gladly taken you
as my final disciple.

157
00:10:23,417 --> 00:10:26,041
Then I wouldn't have had to let
that old geezer Mu En snatch you away.

158
00:10:26,917 --> 00:10:27,917
Senior Du, mind your words.

159
00:10:28,792 --> 00:10:30,291
A teacher for a day
is a father for life.

160
00:10:31,208 --> 00:10:34,291
Even if Teacher is no longer with us,
I will not switch allegiances.

161
00:10:36,125 --> 00:10:37,791
You don't need to be displeased.

162
00:10:38,333 --> 00:10:42,124
Even if Mu En were still alive,
I would still address him that way.

163
00:10:42,583 --> 00:10:45,874
If not for him, my elder brother
would not have died.

164
00:10:47,417 --> 00:10:48,499
Senior Du Bubai,

165
00:10:48,875 --> 00:10:50,707
seems to have lost his former vigor.

166
00:10:51,542 --> 00:10:55,499
Even when facing the Beast God Di Tian,
he was never this dejected.

167
00:10:55,875 --> 00:10:58,666
Enough, that's all ancient history.

168
00:10:59,375 --> 00:11:00,375
Lead the way.

169
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,000
Alright.

170
00:11:02,292 --> 00:11:04,541
Second Soul Skill: Simulation.

171
00:11:14,250 --> 00:11:16,957
Group invisibility.

172
00:11:20,042 --> 00:11:21,042
Fortune.

173
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:41,582
Once we reach Mingdu,
everyone changes their appearance.

174
00:11:41,958 --> 00:11:43,916
Disperse and settle in.

175
00:11:45,208 --> 00:11:46,416
Groups of three.

176
00:11:47,042 --> 00:11:50,166
Maintain contact using the prepared
Communication Soul Tools.

177
00:11:50,583 --> 00:11:52,416
Use coded language when contacting.

178
00:11:57,542 --> 00:12:00,291
Yuhao and Tang Wutong, stick with me.

179
00:12:02,625 --> 00:12:04,832
The previous Mingdu Explosion
was terrifying.

180
00:12:05,708 --> 00:12:07,791
Yet now, Mingdu has fully recovered.

181
00:12:08,375 --> 00:12:09,375
Moreover,

182
00:12:09,625 --> 00:12:12,082
it exudes a deeper, more dangerous aura.

183
00:12:12,875 --> 00:12:14,457
Like a steel behemoth.

184
00:12:15,458 --> 00:12:16,499
Teacher Xuan said

185
00:12:17,042 --> 00:12:19,541
the most advanced place
for Sun-Moon soul tools

186
00:12:19,875 --> 00:12:20,875
is not Mingde Hall,

187
00:12:21,708 --> 00:12:24,999
but the Royal Worship Hall,
controlled by the royal family.

188
00:12:25,333 --> 00:12:26,874
Also called the Royal Research Institute.

189
00:12:28,542 --> 00:12:30,666
Nearly all Class 9 soul engineers

190
00:12:30,958 --> 00:12:32,416
in the Sun-Moon Empire
are members of this institute.

191
00:12:33,417 --> 00:12:35,957
With it, the foundation of the
Sun-Moon Empire remains secure.

192
00:12:56,958 --> 00:12:57,582
Long Shangtian!

193
00:13:05,542 --> 00:13:08,791
Precious treasures...

194
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:12,666
Sun and Moon in tandem,
Imperial Heaven's blessing.

195
00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:15,457
Sacrifice to Heaven Ceremony,
national fortune prospers.

196
00:13:15,875 --> 00:13:18,624
Breaking ground, expanding borders,
prestige spreads far and wide.

197
00:13:18,625 --> 00:13:19,957
Your Majesty's merits shine
bright as the sun and moon.

198
00:13:19,958 --> 00:13:21,166
It's those Royal Guards again.

199
00:13:21,167 --> 00:13:21,874
It's those Royal Guards again.

200
00:13:22,042 --> 00:13:25,541
How hateful! They treat us
like less than human.

201
00:13:25,708 --> 00:13:28,957
Recently, His Majesty is to hold
the Sacrifice to Heaven Ceremony.

202
00:13:29,333 --> 00:13:32,874
These Royal Guards have been leaving
the palace grounds frequently.

203
00:13:32,958 --> 00:13:34,332
But it's we who suffer for it.

204
00:13:36,292 --> 00:13:37,332
The Royal Guards—

205
00:13:38,458 --> 00:13:41,416
their soul tool configuration rivals
the Hand of the Nation-Protector.

206
00:13:41,792 --> 00:13:44,957
Just how much hidden depth
does the Sun-Moon Empire possess?

207
00:13:45,958 --> 00:13:49,124
Detection soul tools cover nearly
the entire city of Mingdu.

208
00:13:50,042 --> 00:13:52,957
It seems the Sun-Moon Empire
takes this ceremony very seriously.

209
00:14:01,667 --> 00:14:03,832
Good evening, Sir and Madam.

210
00:14:07,333 --> 00:14:10,041
Huo Yuhao, the Pavilion Master requests your presence.

211
00:14:16,417 --> 00:14:17,499
Enter.

212
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:24,291
Sit.

213
00:14:26,458 --> 00:14:30,041
Well? Did you find anything
on your stroll outside?

214
00:14:31,125 --> 00:14:33,707
Aside from detection soul tools
blanketing the entire city,

215
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:35,832
there is nothing unusual within Mingdu.

216
00:14:47,875 --> 00:14:52,749
The imperial son born to Xu Tianran
and Orange is named Xu Yunhan.

217
00:14:53,208 --> 00:14:56,707
Shortly after his full moon ceremony,
Xu Tianran established him as Crown Prince.

218
00:14:57,375 --> 00:14:59,707
Senior Du, why tell me all this?

219
00:15:00,458 --> 00:15:03,041
The Crown Prince represents
a nation's future.

220
00:15:03,667 --> 00:15:08,874
Since Xu Tianran is disabled,
having a Crown Prince is even more critical.

221
00:15:09,667 --> 00:15:11,249
After establishing the heir,

222
00:15:11,375 --> 00:15:15,791
dissenting voices from the royal family
quickly vanished.

223
00:15:16,375 --> 00:15:17,957
And the Empress, Orange,

224
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:21,207
possesses outstanding military talent
and illustrious battle merits.

225
00:15:21,208 --> 00:15:23,332
She has become the Commander-in-Chief
of the Three Armies.

226
00:15:23,750 --> 00:15:27,124
This has made Xu Tianran's throne
even more secure.

227
00:15:28,167 --> 00:15:31,749
Xu Tianran seized power through coup,
so his foundation was originally unstable.

228
00:15:32,833 --> 00:15:34,457
Yet through this series of actions,

229
00:15:34,833 --> 00:15:36,916
he has become the emperor in Sun-Moon's
history

230
00:15:36,958 --> 00:15:39,166
with the most stable imperial authority.

231
00:15:41,625 --> 00:15:43,624
We came to Mingdu this time

232
00:15:43,875 --> 00:15:47,749
not only to assassinate Xu Tianran,
but also for another mission.

233
00:15:48,542 --> 00:15:49,542
Another mission?

234
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:57,324
[Huo Yuhao in Disguise]

235
00:15:57,645 --> 00:16:02,125
[Tang Wutong in Disguise]

236
00:16:03,167 --> 00:16:04,167
The operation is named...

237
00:16:04,208 --> 00:16:05,457
"Destroy Emperor Operation."

238
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:06,749
Groups of three.

239
00:16:06,792 --> 00:16:10,041
Once in Mingdu, everyone changes
their appearance.

240
00:16:10,042 --> 00:16:12,207
Wherever the continent reaches
is His Majesty's territory.

241
00:16:12,208 --> 00:16:15,874
Crush the Three Douluo Nations,
unify the continent.

242
00:16:15,875 --> 00:16:20,874
You wolf-hearted cur! Today,
this old man acts on heaven's behalf!

243
00:16:20,958 --> 00:16:22,999
I will collect you, you vile beast!

244
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:25,416
Enough killing, Old Poison.

245
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:53,140
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

